esn't involve any backend calls, with the flow ending in a blueprint generation. I'll include the mock code \"123456\" in the OTP input.\n\n\n**Visualizing Final Output**\n\nI'm now focusing on the final UI report. I plan to use a loading animation during the blueprint generation (e.g., \"Compiling DAG topology...\"). The report itself will showcase the **AI Readiness Score**, with a prominent display (e.g., 87/100, labeled \"AI-Native Leader\"). This is accompanied by the **Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunities**, the **Recommended GFF AI Solution**, and the **Expected Business Impact**. I'm defining the AI Readiness categories to map the score ranges to the corresponding labels. I'm focusing on ensuring it looks premium.\n\n\n"}}
